Tatiyaṁ. 
3. Anuttariyavagga Himavantasutta ^n24 “Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu himavantaṁ pabbatarājaṁ padāleyya, ko pana vādo chavāya avijjāya. 
